#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:812 templates/manager/wp/single.html:826
msgid "Shuffle Salts"
msgstr "ສຸ່ມຄ່າ Salts ໃໝ່"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:818
msgid ""
"WordPress salts are random strings stored in wp-config.php file that are "
"used for the password hashing process. By periodically changing your keys "
"and salts, you make it even harder for hackers to get their hands on your "
"salts."
msgstr ""
"WordPress salts ແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມສຸ່ມທີ່ເກັບໄວ້ໃນໄຟລ໌ wp-config.php "
"ເພື່ອໃຊ້ໃນຂະບວນການເຂົ້າລະຫັດຜ່ານ. ການປ່ຽນແປງຄ່າເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເປັນປະຈຳ "
"ຈະຊ່ວຍເພີ່ມຄວາມປອດໄພຈາກການຖືກແຮັກຂໍ້ມູນ."

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:821
msgid ""
"Note: changing salts will automatically log out all logged-in users and "
"force them to log in again."
msgstr ""
"ໝາຍເຫດ: ການປ່ຽນ salts "
"ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ທັງໝົດທີ່ກຳລັງເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບຢູ່ຖືກອອກຈາກລະບົບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ແລະ"
" ຕ້ອງເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບໃໝ່."

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:875
msgid "Check Integrity"
msgstr "ກວດສອບຄວາມສົມບູນ"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:881
msgid ""
"If you suspect that this site is infected by malware, check the integrity of"
" WordPress core files or Plugins by verifying them against their reference "
"checksums from wordpress.org."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານສົງໄສວ່າເວັບໄຊທ໌ຖືກມັລແວ (Malware) ໂຈມຕີ, "
"ທ່ານສາມາດກວດສອບຄວາມສົມບູນຂອງໄຟລ໌ຫຼັກ WordPress ຫຼື ປລັກອິນ "
"ໂດຍການປຽບທຽບກັບຄ່າ Checksums ມາດຕະຖານຈາກ wordpress.org."

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:885
msgid "Check WP Core"
msgstr "ກວດສອບໄຟລ໌ຫຼັກ WP"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:887
msgid "Check All Plugins"
msgstr "ກວດສອບປລັກອິນທັງໝົດ"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:907
msgid "Checking integrity of WP Core files... Please wait."
msgstr "ກຳລັງກວດສອບຄວາມສົມບູນຂອງໄຟລ໌ຫຼັກ WP... ກະລຸນາລໍຖ້າ."

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:938
msgid "An error occurred while verifying checksums."
msgstr ""

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:954
msgid "Checking integrity for all WordPress plugins... Please wait."
msgstr "ກຳລັງກວດສອບຄວາມສົມບູນຂອງປລັກອິນ WordPress ທັງໝົດ... ກະລຸນາລໍຖ້າ."

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:987
msgid "An error occurred while verifying plugins checksums."
msgstr ""

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1027
msgid "Reinstall"
msgstr "ຕິດຕັ້ງໃໝ່"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1033
msgid ""
"If checksums fail to match, you can quickly reinstall WordPress core files "
"or all plugins without affecting your site content."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກຄ່າ checksum ບໍ່ກົງກັນ, ທ່ານສາມາດຕິດຕັ້ງໄຟລ໌ຫຼັກ WordPress ຫຼື "
"ປລັກອິນໃໝ່ໄດ້ທັນທີ ໂດຍບໍ່ມີຜົນກະທົບຕໍ່ເນື້ອໃນເວັບໄຊທ໌ຂອງທ່ານ."

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1037
