#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1621
msgid ""
"The options below allow you to manage the native WordPress debugging tools, "
"enabling and disabling these tools in the wp-config.php file. It is not "
"recommended to use these options on production websites since they are meant"
" for development and test installations. Refer to"
msgstr ""
"ຕົວເລືອກລຸ່ມນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຈັດການເຄື່ອງມືດີບັກຂອງ WordPress ໂດຍການເປີດ ຫຼື "
"ປິດການໃຊ້ງານໃນໄຟລ໌ wp-config.php. "
"ບໍ່ແນະນຳໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໃນເວັບໄຊທ໌ທີ່ໃຊ້ງານຈິງ "
"ເພາະມັນມີໄວ້ສຳລັບການພັດທະນາ ແລະ ທົດສອບເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ອ້າງອີງຈາກ"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1621
msgid "Debugging in WordPress"
msgstr "ການດີບັກໃນ WordPress"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1621
msgid "article for more information on these options."
msgstr "ບົດຄວາມສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບຕົວເລືອກເຫຼົ່ານີ້."

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1636 templates/manager/wp/single.html:1643
msgid "WP_DEBUG"
msgstr "WP_DEBUG"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1637
msgid "WordPress debug mode."
msgstr "ໂໝດດີບັກຂອງ WordPress."

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1646
msgid "Enable WP_DEBUG mode"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ໂໝດ WP_DEBUG"

