#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1694
msgid "Enable WP_DEBUG_DISPLAY"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ WP_DEBUG_DISPLAY"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1708 templates/manager/wp/single.html:1715
msgid "SCRIPT_DEBUG"
msgstr "SCRIPT_DEBUG"

#: templates/manager/wp/single.html:1709
msgid ""
"Force WordPress to use the non-minified versions of core CSS and JavaScript "
"files. This is useful when you are testing changes made to .js and .css "
"files."
msgstr ""
"ບັງຄັບໃຫ້ WordPress ໃຊ້ໄຟລ໌ CSS ແລະ JavaScript ຫຼັກໃນເວີຊັນທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ບີບອັດ. "
